    "body": "In my app, when i send a transaction, i sleep for ten seconds, then send  an eth.getTransaction(<hash>) request. My app needs to follow up with a transaction to see if it was included in a block and was mined without a revert. I'm trying to optimize it in a way that does not require a sleep and multiple eth.getTransaction(<hash>) calls.",
