    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "If you don't want do polling then you can use the subscription [API](https://geth.ethereum.org/docs/rpc/pubsub). There's no notification for a tx being mined but you can either:\r\n\r\n- Subscribe to a log event your tx emits that you're interested in\r\n- Or, subscribe to `newHeads` which gives you new mined blocks and check to see if they include your tx",
